       <h2> <a rel="external" href="http://www.newyorker.com/humor/issuecartoons/2013/01/28/cartoons_20130121#slide=13">Touchscreen</a><span class="external"></span> </h2> 
      </header> 
      <section class="info"> 
       <p> Publicado <abbr class="timeago" title="2013-08-12 10:06:50">2013-08-12 10:06:50</abbr> en <a href="/t/Humor">Humor</a> </p> 
